layers.name: The National Geographic Society is a global nonprofit organization committed to exploring and protecting our planet. We are not just a magazine and a tv channel! The interaction of animals with their environments is the engine that keeps the planet healthy for all of us. But for many species, time is running out. That's why National Geographic, along with photographer Joel Sartore, is dedicated to finding solutions to save them. But for many species, time is running out.
